01:01:39,680 --> 01:01:40,079
you know?

912
01:01:40,079 --> 01:01:47,839
So, no faster way to demoralize people or to hire the wrong people than promising things that are actually out of your control.

913
01:01:47,839 --> 01:01:53,200
Being honest and upfront about who you are as a company, about what you're able to promise,

914
01:01:53,200 --> 01:02:01,280
like all of that is actually it's very hard work, but it's so important because so much is out of your control and you need to hire people that are cool with that.

