01:09:37,279 --> 01:09:38,960
I basically develop a theory about someone.

1011
01:09:38,960 --> 01:09:42,000
I think this person is capable of this kind of thing.

1012
01:09:42,000 --> 01:09:45,040
And then piece by piece, it doesn't have to be like a whole job or whole project.

