01:09:45,040 --> 01:09:47,759
It can just be like uh, you know, an incremental experiment.

1014
01:09:47,759 --> 01:09:52,080
I'm going to see if they can do this without, you know, with less guidance or support from me.

1015
01:09:52,080 --> 01:09:53,600
I'm going to give them a bigger project.

